6 Hours Ago The case had been adjourned to February 2, 2022.  There has been widespread outrage over Hanifa's murder, with #JusticeForHanifa trending on social media for days.  The victim was kidnapped on December 4, 2021 and murdered two weeks later; her body was dismembered and buried on her former school's premises.  Tanko was arrested by the police while trying to collect the N6million ransom he demanded from her parents. 